{"tid":253903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回歸20年‧舞照跳】玩家蒲足20年：舞照跳？一早冇咗啦","createTime":"2017-05-22T18:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T16:15:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e03d2d65cbbf468d6bfb18372a91fd769b5ed6fb","tid":253903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728344&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728344%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=vmfswHDa%2FdeqHnVAcoF6BTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=804ce1e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56728344%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=ca4b632c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56728344&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170522/large/1495457887_6367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170522%2Flarge%2F1495457887_6367.jpg&h=d82ebb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即時突發  2017-05-23 00:40:31 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n「馬照跑、舞照跳」有多重解讀，經濟學家關焯照表示，這句話潛藏着「維持香港資本主義社會和自由經濟不變」的意思，時至今日，他認為這句說話仍然適用，只是沒80年代般繁榮。他分析，鄧小平說出「舞照跳」一句，正值香港經濟蓬勃的80年代，當時本地生產總值每年平均增長達8至10%，不少更有雙位數增長，當時失業率僅2%，屬全民就業，香港與台灣、新加坡、韓國更被稱為「亞洲四小龍」。<br />\n<br />\n手機用戶請觀看：回歸20年‧舞照跳Timeline <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qVHJJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qVHJJY&d=vmfswHDa%2FdeqHnVAcoF6BTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=92d86875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qVHJJY</a><br />\n<br />\n回歸至今20年，從經濟角度上看，香港仍是維持資本主義社會，繼續奉行自由經濟，「舞照跳」依然存在，只是今非昔比。今年香港首季經濟增長僅錄得4.3%，失業率3.2%，該百分比已屬全民就業，但關焯照認為，本港四大經濟支柱產業，包括物流、貿易、旅遊和金融已漸走下坡，變得老化。內地華南地區的工廠陸續搬走、中國經濟放緩，令本港物流和貿易需求下降；至於金融和旅遊業的發展，亦不再像從前具備優勢。<br />\n<br />\n不過從事IT界的玩家蕉仔卻不認同：「仲舞照跳？一早冇咗啦！」自言玩盡香港大小夜總會的他，涉足過大富豪、中國城和富都等大場，當年確實瘋狂上癮，「97年前更加黐咗線，一晚豪花30、40萬是等閒事。」80年代起公司高層每周兩三晚「拉大隊」到夜總會消遣，每晚每人豪花萬元亦面不改容。<br />\n<br />\n回歸後，香港夜總會小姐大多來自內地，「咁點解我唔返大陸玩，嗰度仲平。」他稱自兩、三年前就隨老闆到東莞夜總會見識，花街選秀一幕令他大開眼界，「場內有三層，樓梯企滿幾百位身穿晚裝、化韓妝的小姐，任你揀，5、6個人去，只係7至8萬人民幣，香港一定唔得。」他形容本港夜總會愈做愈霉，現時只餘下小型夜總會，該行業早已成為歷史。"},{"pid":"45cffa16e270e29a636902ff38f386e1d5cade79","tid":253903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17423eb08eb8a28292917d2fcd781cca0f8f58e","tid":253903,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"連 gig 都唔畀攪, 跳老舞咩"},{"pid":"1afbe5f02108ae87e663621be648513f3448256c","tid":253903,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"姐係叫雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903a6cfb9d3e7149c5d7ddc5a12ef9ac928e3265","tid":253903,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:53:22.000Z","msg":"回你老母歸咩<br />\n死毒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3094759937de4e0c03d32b262225b9c38213c21","tid":253903,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連 gig 都唔畀攪, 跳老舞咩</blockquote><br />\n九叔連跳老舞既機會都無呀"},{"pid":"ca4a6d6d8f86099ab2d1f6734a396cf36015afe9","tid":253903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98481624e6e25df586ca66c16c3d805dbbb05ba0","tid":253903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:13